snippet.title: The Dire TRAILER
snippet.description:
I am happy to present the trailer for my upcoming game The Dire 

The Dire is a game in which you play as an urbex vlogger who intends to explore an old estate in the abandoned town of Clover Springs.
However, your urbex adventure doesn't go according to plan; something is wrong with this place
 Many years ago, in this place, a tragedy occurred that was never explained...
 Perhaps you will manage to investigate what happened there, if anything did happen 
-
The Dire is a psychological horror walking simulator. 
available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2664890/The_Dire/
-
-
Voice Actors:
-
Urbex vloger: Aaron Schulman
Radio Host:  Anthony Conner
-
